SUMMARY:CoffeeTue- IC Houston Cafe (22R) -- RSVP required
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\nRide Leader: Bruce Black\
 n\nCoffeeTue rides:\n• A rotating start location\, not a school\n• A p
 redetermined route\n• 25+/- mile routes\n• 13 to 15 mph average pace\n
 • Usually no sweep\n• “short” stop for refreshment/coffee mid-rout
 e at [Houston Cafe](https://www.thehoustoncafe.com/)\n\nClick for [Ride wi
 th GPS](https://routes.lancasterbikeclub.net/cue/__trashed/)\n\nHelmets ar
 e mandatory. No ear buds. Please bring water and a basic repair kit (spare
  tube\, tire levers\, pump/CO2 inflator).\n\nTo eliminate passing around a
  pen and paper waiver\, we require LBC Club membership and Meetup RSVP bel
 ow to join this ride.\n\nBeing on Meetup does not mean you are a club memb
 er. [Join here](https://www.lancasterbikeclub.net/content.aspx?page_id=60&
 club_id=257148).\n\nYour RSVP is your agreement to abide by the club's [Co
 de of Conduct](https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/content.aspx?page_id=2
 2&club_id=257148&module_id=323984) \,\n[Rules of the Road](https://lancbik
 eclub.clubexpress.com/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=325
 159) \, and [Ride Waiver](https://lancasterbikeclub.net/docs.ashx?id=45431
 8)
